class Solution(object):
    def maxOperations(self, s):
        """
        :type s: str
        :rtype: int
        """
        carryOn = 0
        ans = 0
        prev = "0"
        for i in range(len(s)):
            if s[i]=="1":
                prev = "1"
                carryOn += 1
            if s[i]=="0" and prev=="1":
                prev = "0"
                ans+=carryOn
        return ans
